Package: xtdata
Type: Package
Title: Functions to manipulate Quality of Government data and related material
Version: 0.1
Date: 2013-08-05
Author: Francois Briatte <f.briatte@ed.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Francois Briatte <f.briatte@ed.ac.uk>
Description: This package contains a set of functions to download and manipulate
    Quality of Government (QOG) datasets and codebooks. It uses a specification
    for panel data that makes it easy to merge QOG datasets with other series,
    of which a few examples are provided.
    Please turn to http://www.qog.pol.gu.se for details on QOG datasets.
Suggests:
    countrycode,
    foreign,
    ggplot2,
    Hmisc,
    maps,
    plyr,
    WDI
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/briatte/qogdata
LazyData: true
Collate:
    'utils.R'
    'qog.R'
    'xtplot.R'
    'get.R'
    'xt.R'
